         Dormant for D025c+D035 (no live dotnet invocation in tests); becomes
         a live assertion in sub-branch #3 when D025f's PackageReference
         parser ingests it (.csproj at depth 5 → osv-scanner adhoc lockfile). -->
    <PackageReference Include="Newtonsoft.Json" Version="9.0.1" />
  </ItemGroup>

</Project>
